  "slug": "immersive-paintings",
  "title": "Immersive Paintings",
  "description": "Drag and drop, pixelate and hang up beautiful art. On servers too.",
  "body": "<img width=\"872\"\nsrc=\"https://cdn.conczin.net/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,w=872,f=jpeg,q=90/https://cdn.conczin.net/immersive-paintings/banner.jpg\"\nalt=\"Screenshot\"/>\n<p>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/immersive-paintings\">\n<img alt=\"Modrinth\"\nsrc=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Modrinth-NA?style=for-the-badge&logo=modrinth&logoColor=000000&color=00AF5C\">\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/immersive-paintings\">\n<img alt=\"CurseForge\"\nsrc=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/CurseForge-NA?style=for-the-badge&logo=curseforge&logoColor=000000&color=F16436\">\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://discord.gg/agxcvAdj2a\">\n<img alt=\"Discord\"\nsrc=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Discord-NA?style=for-the-badge&logo=discord&logoColor=000000&color=5865F2\">\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://github.com/Luke100000/ImmersivePaintings\">\n<img alt=\"Github\"\nsrc=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Github-NA?style=for-the-badge&logo=github&color=181717\">\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://crowdin.com/project/immersive-collection\">\n<img alt=\"Translate via Crowdin\"\nsrc=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Crowdin-NA?style=for-the-badge&logo=crowdin&color=2E3340\">\n</a>\n</p>\n\n<p>\nTired of the overly pixelated, limited amount of paintings without a proper selection GUI?\nImmersive Paintings allows users to create their own, Minecraft-stylized paintings via drag and drop, screenshots,\nor by providing a URL.\nNo resource pack required, Multiplayer friendly and easy to use.\n</p>\n\n<p>The mod offers a simple yet powerful GUI to select your paintings, those from fellow players or those provided via\noptional datapacks. Default datapack available for a quick start!</p>\n<img width=\"872\"\nsrc=\"https://cdn.conczin.net/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,w=872,f=jpeg,q=90/https://cdn.conczin.net/immersive-paintings/screenshots/selector.jpg\"\nalt=\"Screenshot\"/>\n\n<p>The creation menu allows you to quickly pixelate your images and apply post-effects and dithering to make them look\nlike they fit into Minecraft, without much fiddling around.</p>\n<img width=\"872\"\nsrc=\"https://cdn.conczin.net/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,w=872,f=jpeg,q=90/https://cdn.conczin.net/immersive-paintings/screenshots/editor.jpg\"\nalt=\"Screenshot\"/>\n\n<p>But what's a fancy painting without a fancy frame? Select from different styles and a lot of materials to put your\nartwork into a better focus.</p>\n<img width=\"872\"\nsrc=\"https://cdn.conczin.net/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,w=872,f=jpeg,q=90/https://cdn.conczin.net/immersive-paintings/screenshots/frames.jpg\"\nalt=\"Screenshot\"/>\n\n<p>Using smart level of details, caching and lazy streaming of data the performance impact is not noticeable.</p>\n<img width=\"872\"\nsrc=\"https://cdn.conczin.net/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,w=872,f=jpeg,q=90/https://cdn.conczin.net/immersive-paintings/screenshots/multi.jpg\"\nalt=\"Screenshot\"/>\n\n<p>Available with glowing paint as well!</p>\n<img width=\"872\"\nsrc=\"https://cdn.conczin.net/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,w=872,f=jpeg,q=90/https://cdn.conczin.net/immersive-paintings/screenshots/glow.jpg\"\nalt=\"Screenshot\"/>\n\n<p>Your image has transparency? No problem, use a graffiti and spray it on every wall!</p>\n<img width=\"872\"\nsrc=\"https://cdn.conczin.net/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,w=872,f=jpeg,q=90/https://cdn.conczin.net/immersive-paintings/screenshots/alpha.jpg\"\nalt=\"Screenshot\"/>\n\n<p>And here is the crafting recipe.</p>\n\n\n\n\n<p><img src=\"https://api-rk.conczin.net/mcr/recipes?minecraft_version=1.20.1&locations=immersive_paintings%3A.%2A&dependencies=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2FLuke100000%2FImmersivePaintings%2Ftree%2F1.20.1&resolution=48&animated=False&row_width=835\" alt=\"Generated Recipes Image\"/></p>\n\n<p>\n<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/joy-of-painting\">Joy of Painting</a> compatible!\nJust slap a canvas on a painting to showcase!\n</p>\n<img width=\"872\"\nsrc=\"https://cdn.conczin.net/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,w=872,f=jpeg,q=90/https://cdn.conczin.net/immersive-paintings/screenshots/joy.jpg\"\nalt=\"Screenshot\"/>\n\n<h1>For Server Admins</h1>\n<p>\nImmersive Paintings has to transfer and store images, on a server they may get quite a lot. If your server suffers\nfrom low bandwidth, or storage space, take a look at the\n<a href=\"https://github.com/Luke100000/ImmersivePaintings/wiki/Config\">config file</a>.\nIt allows a few limitations for users and bandwidth throttling to adjust to your need.\n</p>\n\n<h1>Datapacks</h1>\n<p>\nOptionally, share packs of paintings using\n<a href=\"https://github.com/Luke100000/ImmersivePaintings/wiki/Custom-Paintings\">datapacks</a>.\n</p>\n\n<h1>Translations</h1>\n<p>\nYou would like to have the mod in your language? Help translate the mod on\n<a href=\"https://crowdin.com/project/immersive-collection\">Crowdin</a>\n</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<h1>Immersive Collection</h1>\n<p>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/immersive-armors\">\n<img width=\"275\"\nsrc=\"https://api-rk.conczin.net/embed?title=Immersive%20Armors&description=A%20lot%20of%20unique%20and%20vanilla-faithful%20armor%20sets.&icon_url=https%3A//cdn.conczin.net/immersive-armors/icon.png&width=275&height=100&background_color=16181c\"\nalt=\"Immersive Armors\"/>\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/immersive-aircraft\">\n<img width=\"275\"\nsrc=\"https://api-rk.conczin.net/embed?title=Immersive%20Aircraft&description=A%20bunch%20of%20rustic%20aircraft%20to%20travel%2C%20transport%2C%20and%20explore%21&icon_url=https%3A//cdn.conczin.net/immersive-aircraft/icon.png&width=275&height=100&background_color=16181c\"\nalt=\"Immersive Aircraft\"/>\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/immersive-melodies\">\n<img width=\"275\"\nsrc=\"https://api-rk.conczin.net/embed?title=Immersive%20Melodies&description=Play%20custom%20melodies%20on%20various%20instruments%20and%20annoy%20your%20friends%21&icon_url=https%3A//cdn.conczin.net/immersive-melodies/icon.png&width=275&height=100&background_color=16181c\"\nalt=\"Immersive Melodies\"/>\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/immersive-paintings\">\n<img width=\"275\"\nsrc=\"https://api-rk.conczin.net/embed?title=Immersive%20Paintings&description=Drag%20and%20drop%2C%20pixelate%20and%20hang%20up%20beautiful%20art.&icon_url=https%3A//cdn.conczin.net/immersive-paintings/icon.png&width=275&height=100&background_color=16181c\"\nalt=\"Immersive Paintings\"/>\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/immersive-optimization\">\n<img width=\"275\"\nsrc=\"https://api-rk.conczin.net/embed?title=Immersive%20Optimization&description=A%20lightweight%20entity-tick-scheduler%20for%20doubling%20your%20TPS.&icon_url=https%3A//cdn.conczin.net/immersive-optimization/icon.png&width=275&height=100&background_color=16181c\"\nalt=\"Immersive Optimization\"/>\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/selectivebounds\">\n<img width=\"275\"\nsrc=\"https://api-rk.conczin.net/embed?title=SelectiveBounds&description=Hides%20the%20ugly%20block%20selection%20outline%20when%20not%20relevant.&icon_url=https%3A//cdn.conczin.net/selectivebounds/icon.png&width=275&height=100&background_color=16181c\"\nalt=\"SelectiveBounds\"/>\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/man-of-many-planes\">\n<img width=\"275\"\nsrc=\"https://api-rk.conczin.net/embed?title=Man%20of%20Many%20Planes&description=A%20set%20of%20additional%20aircraft%20for%20Immersive%20Aircraft%20with%20Create%20support%20in%20mind.&icon_url=https%3A//cdn.conczin.net/man-of-many-planes/icon.png&width=275&height=100&background_color=16181c\"\nalt=\"Man of Many Planes\"/>\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/immersive-machinery\">\n<img width=\"275\"\nsrc=\"https://api-rk.conczin.net/embed?title=Immersive%20Machinery&description=A%20bunch%20of%20rustic%20machinery%20to%20transport%2C%20mine%2C%20and%20automate%20things.&icon_url=https%3A//cdn.conczin.net/immersive-machinery/icon.png&width=275&height=100&background_color=16181c\"\nalt=\"Immersive Machinery\"/>\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/immersive-furniture\">\n<img width=\"275\"\nsrc=\"https://api-rk.conczin.net/embed?title=Immersive%20Furniture&description=Create%20custom%20and%20fancy%20furniture%20in-game%20or%20choose%20from%20a%20vast%20online%20library.&icon_url=https%3A//cdn.conczin.net/immersive-furniture/icon.png&width=275&height=100&background_color=16181c\"\nalt=\"Immersive Furniture\"/>\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/immersive-gateways\">\n<img width=\"275\"\nsrc=\"https://api-rk.conczin.net/embed?title=Immersive%20Gateways&description=Mysterious%2C%20long-forgotten%20portals%20scattered%20across%20the%20Overworld.&icon_url=https%3A//cdn.conczin.net/immersive-gateways/icon.png&width=275&height=100&background_color=16181c\"\nalt=\"Immersive Gateways\"/>\n</a></p>\n\n<h1>Addons</h1>\n<p>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/immersive-paintings-faithful-addon\">\n<img width=\"275\"\nsrc=\"https://api-rk.conczin.net/embed?title=Faithful%20Addon&description=32px%20texture%20pack%20addon%20for%20Faithful.&icon_url=https%3A//media.forgecdn.net/avatars/thumbnails/629/725/64/64/638028066470632891.jpeg&width=275&height=100&background_color=16181c\"\nalt=\"Faithful Addon\"/>\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/arids-immersive-resprites\">\n<img width=\"275\"\nsrc=\"https://api-rk.conczin.net/embed?title=Arids%20Immersive%20Resprites&description=Resprites%20for%20the%20Immersive%20Melodies%20and%20Immersive%20Paintings%20mods%21&icon_url=https%3A//cdn.conczin.net/common/icons/arids-immersive-resprites.webp&width=275&height=100&background_color=16181c\"\nalt=\"Arids Immersive Resprites\"/>\n</a></p>\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.conczin.net/common/pixel.png?immersive_pages_hash=f79ed7591f3496f8580139e47ae744c3\" alt=\"The page hash for easier page deployment.\"/>",
